test.sorted.bam is the example input file. Make sure to have "human_g1k_v37.fasta" availabe

*to create the pbam file use below

	sh bam2pbam.sh -in ../../test_data/test.sorted.bam -r human_g1k_v37.fasta

this will create ../../test_data/test.sorted.bam.p.bam and ../../test_data/test.sorted.bam.diff files

*to go back to the bam file from pbam file

	sh pbam2bam.sh -in ../../test_data/test.sorted.bam.p.bam -r human_g1k_v37.fasta -p ../../test_data/ -d test.sorted.bam.diff

this will create ../../test_data/test.sorted.bam.p.bam.bam file
